text.tspan: Sex gap in life expectancy at different ages, United Kingdom

The sex gap of female minus male
life expectancy
at different ages. Positive values indicate higher life
expectancy among females; negative values indicate higher life expectancy among males.
Data source: Human Mortality Database (2024); UN, World Population Prospects (2024)
